<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416769' id='t-416769'>So we did several attempts
to reach this area,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='421639' id='t-421639'>by land and with a helicopter,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423425' id='t-423425'>but it was really difficult
