 7:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='448723' id='t-448723'>The cave is huge.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450664' id='t-450664'>It's a huge network under the surface
