<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472999' id='t-472999'>So it's really an incredible place.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476047' id='t-476047'>And we named it Imawarì Yeuta.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478612' id='t-478612'>That means, in the Pemón indigenous
